            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">25/10/95. ¶  ¶ You will have probably have learned, dear Miss Hussey by this time of the very sad event, which deprived us one of our most genial friends! Early this week poor J. Bracebridge Wilson pa...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">95.10.25</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Jessie Hussey</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">State Library of South Australia, Adelaide.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="Table1">
               <row>
